<br>
I currently at any given moment can taunt the hell out of most mobs and i DO get the aggro.<br>
<br>
Pallies rock for taunting, and the guy who posted about 2hs, does not know how to use his spells to get the aggro.  Yaulp, stun, strike, flash of light and root...ALL of them create aggro.  You want to be the main tank mem your 2 stun spells and hotkey your DW bracer and start stunning the F*ck out of the mob...you will get beat down to your hearts content.  Trust me on this..i have experimented with 2hs, 2hb, 2hb and 1hs....any one hander with a couple stun spells memmed will get you the aggro if you use your spells right.<br>
<br>
<br>
just  my 2cp.<br>
<br>
hope this helps,<br>
<br>
Reeiyna DelaTierra<br>
54th Paladin<br>
Server of Divine Legion<br>
Humble follower of Tunare<br>
