<br>
FD is a great wepon, and if i can say almost a must on paladins. 35 dmg, 40 dly, with stun dd proc and stats is great for a taunter.<br>
<br>
I also realize that spells can taunt, but if you are with a warrior in group only hitin the Taunt button they can get much more atention than many spells. Its really hard to fight for agro with a warrior using SotM that is my case, and i have good haste, usually better then others.<br>
<br>
